  Electrostatic Interaction:            -0.088317748509709         -2.4032           -55.42          -231.88
 (Electrostatic Interaction =
  Delta V_elstat in the BB paper)
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Steric Interaction:              0.102984924376710          2.8024            64.62           270.39
 (Total Steric Interaction =
  Delta E^0 in the BB paper)

